{"tid":2226244,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司多數喺一日咩時間炒人？","createTime":"2020-10-02T02:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T13:23:26.000Z","uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"168809c5f4b2d48d6d23c5b687502f10ab8cf363","tid":2226244,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:05:38.000Z","msg":"答案：朝早10點05分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日新冠肺炎疫情持續，很多公司為節流而宣布解僱員工。據非正式統計，如被解僱的員工，通常會在上午10時05分得知消息。<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼公司一般在上午10時05分解僱員工呢？因為上班時間通常在上午9時或之前，10時左右大部分員工已在公司。公司高層一般不是即日決定解僱員工，由於高層或老闆通常會稍晚一點回到公司，他們上班時隨即會把解僱信傳至人事部，此時已是10時左右。人事部員工一般會再用5分鐘把解僱信傳遞至被解僱的員工，加上公司要預留較充裕時間讓被解僱的員工執拾個人物品，即日內離開公司，所以10時05分是員工被解僱的「黃金時間」了。"},{"pid":"98ea3fc79c09fd2ca6301d261d42034de8746a2b","tid":2226244,"uid":192748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:07:39.000Z","msg":"返咗嗰一個鐘零5分鐘計唔計糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38097d3df55717a38d0bd3a0de0b493ccf52feb1","tid":2226244,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次見到個供緊樓既柒頭比人炒<br />\n<br />\n男人老狗四十歲即場喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b33fa69d705cde4e6dd17525b7e76fd625929f2","tid":2226244,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38097d3df55717a38d0bd3a0de0b493ccf52feb1","tid":2226244,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次見到個供緊樓既柒頭比人炒<br />\n<br />\n男人老狗四十歲即場喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:13:32.000Z","msg":"幾點炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/no